summary: An ordinance relating to, and providing for, the sale and conveyance of a triangular tract of land lying north of the north margin of North 80th Street, east of the east margin of the alley produced south, as platted in Lakeview Heights Addition to the City of Seattle, and southwesterly of the southwesterly margin of North Green Lake Way, as established by Ordinance No. 51536, and providing for the method of payment therefor.
